t hosts a competition called the New Play Development Program.<ref>{{Cite book|title=Canadian Mosaic II: Six Plays|author=Aviva Ravel|publisher=[[Dundurn Group]]|year=1996|isbn=0889242747|page=256|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4KwQBfNDbEsC&pg=PA256&lpg=PA256&dq=%22Alberta+Playwrights+Network%22&source=bl&ots=Zq5B-hmC6W&sig=IjKhyaFS6Jz94KpkeEL3Gv3wjzg&hl=en&sa=X&ei=GIsdUJyHFoaQ8wT1toCoAg&ved=0CD0Q6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=%22Alberta%20Playwrights%20Network%22&f=false|accessdate=August 4, 2012}}</ref> Gordon Pengilly is a [[dramaturge]] for the Alberta Playwrights Network,<ref>{{Cite book|page=184|author=Robin C. Whittaker|title=Hot Thespian Action!: Ten Première Plays from Walterdale Playhouse|publisher=[[Athabasca University Press]]|year=2008|isbn=1897425260|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xieLrkQhaYUC&pg=PA569&lpg=PA569&dq=%22Alberta+Playwrights+Network%22&source=bl&ots=mneiQvq_M8&sig=h7ibwrwOtl0pb-6BXgpOlDkiTY4&hl=en&sa=X&ei=xIsdUIaWIpGo8QTx8YFA&ved=0CEwQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q=%22Alberta%20Playwrights%20Network%22&f=false|accessdate=August 4, 2012}}</ref> as is Gisèle Villeneuve.<ref>{{Cite book|title=Dictionnaire des Artistes et des Auteurs Francophones de l'Ouest Canadien|author=Gilles Cadrin|author2=Paul Dubé|author3=Laurent Godbout|publisher=Presses Université Laval|year=1998|page=326|isbn=2763775667|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Nj6UzViNikgC&dq=%22Alberta+Playwrights+Network%22&source=gbs_navlinks_s|accessdate=August 4, 2012}}</ref> [[Sharon Pollock]] was elected president of the Alberta Playwrights Network in 1998.<ref>{{Cite book|title=Sharon Pollack: Essays on Her Works|author=Anna Nothof|publisher=[[Guernica Editions]]|year=2000|isbn=1550711083|page=181|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Iw3KqhdtllgC&pg=PA181&lpg=PA181&dq=%22Alberta+Playwrights+Network%22&source=bl&ots=Ci_w-4L9E7&sig=DqSpkfG7nfmvpARwUlyLrg29QRA&hl=en&sa=X&ei=VIwdUNaqI8jm6wG1r4AQ&ved=0CDEQ6AEwADgK#v=onepage&q=%22Alberta%20Playwrights%20Network%22&f=false|accessdate=August 4, 2012}}</ref> Sandra Dempsey had previously been the president.<ref>{{Cite book|title=Behind the Scenes: A Canadian Scene Book|author=Mary Ross|author2=Ron Cameron|page=36|publisher=[[Dundurn Group]]|year=1990|isbn=0889241945|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=eFucLlJ_s3oC&dq=%22Alberta+Playwrights+Network%22&source=gbs_navlinks_s|accessdate=August 4, 2012}}</ref> The Alberta Playwrights Network supported Katherine Koller in writing such plays as ''The Seed Savers''.<ref>{{Cite book|title=Voices of the Land: The Seed Savers and Other Plays|author=Katherine Koller|publisher=[[Athabasca University Press]]|year=2012|isbn=1926836936|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=R0nQdKZMmtkC&dq=%22Alberta+Playwrights+Network%22&source=gbs_navlinks_s|accessdate=August 4, 2012}}</ref> The association produces a newsletter called ''Rave Review''.<ref>{{Cite book|page=298|title=Making Theatre: A Life of Sharon Pollock|author=Sherrill Grace|publisher=[[Talonbooks]]|year=2008|isbn=0889225869|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZbofAQAAIAAJ&q=%22Alberta+Playwrights+Network%22&dq=%22Alberta+Playwrights+Network%22&source=bl&ots=4MTq6z90EK&sig=7LZrS8qUlZonNvUOmcyVKsbYn34&hl=en&sa=X&ei=HI0dUKuhKdLU6QGw54Fw&ved=0CDcQ6AEwATgU|accessdate=August 4, 2012}}</ref> The Alberta Playwrights Network has also engaged in playwright exchanges with other associations, including the Saskatchewan Playwrights Centre and the Playwrights Theatre Centre.<ref>{{Cite book|title=Developing Nation: New Play Creation in English-Speaking Canada|author=Bruce Barton|publisher=[[Theatre Communications Group]]|year=2010|isbn=0887545939|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oRgqAQAAIAAJ&q=%22Alberta+Playwrights+Network%22&dq=%22Alberta+Playwrights+Network%22&source=bl&ots=8hlpl9-UNu&sig=XR4Iho2nu313KRJ02evwa0yQZAg&hl=en&sa=X&ei=TY0dUISIKaet6QG3tYGoBQ&ved=0CFAQ6AEwBjgU|accessdate=August 4, 2012}}</ref> The Alberta Playwrights Network also presented an annual award with Scripts At Work called the Scripts At Work/Alberta Playwrights Network Award.<ref>{{Cite journal|author=Mark Weber|journal=Red Deer Express|title=Author explores plight of Malaysian refugees|date=July 14, 2010}}</ref>
